; Coverage for commodity.cc deep commodity comparison
; Two commodities with same base name but different annotations

2024/01/01 Buy Lot A
    Assets:Stock    5 AAPL {$100.00} [2024/01/01] (lot-a)
    Assets:Cash

2024/02/01 Buy Lot B
    Assets:Stock    3 AAPL {$100.00} [2024/02/01] (lot-b)
    Assets:Cash

test bal --lots Assets:Stock
5 AAPL {$100} [2024/01/01] (lot-a)
3 AAPL {$100} [2024/02/01] (lot-b)  Assets:Stock
end test
